                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. Winds south to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h tending east to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h in the early morning. Overnight temperatures falling to between 11 and 17 with daytime temperatures reaching 23 to 30.</text>
